==English==

===Noun===
# a piece or [[lock]] of curling hair; a [[ringlet]]
# a [[spin]] making the trajectory of an object [[curve]]
# {{weightlifting}}: Any exercise performed by bending the [[arm]]s or [[leg]]s on the [[exertion]], especially those that train the [[biceps]].

===Verb===
# to cause to curve
# to make into a curl
# {{calculus}} A [[vector field]] denoting the rotation per unit area of a given vector field.

